{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"prepareForReuse","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The default implementation of this method does nothing. You can override it in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"your custom annotation view implementation to put the view in a known state","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"before it is returned to your map view delegate.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"prepareForReuse"}],"role":"symbol","title":"prepareForReuse","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L117"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)prepareForReuse","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"prepareForReuse"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/prepareForReuse","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/prepareforreuse"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Called when the view is removed from the reuse queue."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/prepareForReuse":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"prepareForReuse","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/prepareForReuse","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/prepareforreuse","abstract":[{"text":"Called when the view is removed from the reuse queue.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"prepareForReuse","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"prepareForReuse","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"}}}